import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='miles', kde=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of miles driven?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Miles Driven')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x='miles', y='gas', data=data)
    ax.set_xlabel('Miles')
    ax.set_ylabel('Gas')
    ax.xaxis.label.set_rotation(0)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the average gas consumption per mile?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='ignore')
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='year', y='miles', data=data)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        chart.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the trend in miles driven over the years?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['gas'] = pd.to_numeric(data['gas'], errors='coerce')
    chart = sns.histplot(data=data, x='gas', kde=True)
    chart.set(xlabel='Gas Consumption (gallons)', ylabel='Frequency')
    chart.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of gas consumption?', wrap=True)
    plt.axvline(data['gas'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Mean: {data["gas"].mean():0.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

chart = plot(data)
